# Syntropy Suite

Plugin roots (relative to repo root):
- `./delivery-team-plugin/delivery-team-plugin/`
- `./librarian-plugin/librarian-plugin/`
- `./research-team-plugin/research-team-plugin/`

Global installs: `~/.claude/skills`, `~/.claude/agents`, `~/.cursor/skills`, `~/.cursor/agents`.

When the user invokes delivery, librarian, or research workflows, use the matching Syntropy skill: `team-intake`, `team-qa`, `team-build`, `team-release`, `team-status`, `librarian`, `team-research`.
